events.name: Flutter Study Jam

venue.name: Chamber of Commerce and Industry Maramures

events.description:
Flutter este un UI kit portabil construit de Google pentru a realiza interfețe native de înaltă calitate pe iOS și Android într-un timp record. Flutter este gratuit și open source, funcționează cu codul deja existent și este folosit de dezvoltatori și organizații din întreaga lume.

Dorești să începeți să construiești aplicații Flutter?
Vino la Flutter Study Jam! Împreună vom parcuge codelaburi Flutter, pregătite de instructorii Google. Vei putea obține o experiență practică cu Flutter și totodată să creezi o aplicație Flutter în timp ce înveți elementele fundamentale.

Adu un laptop! Pentru cea mai bună experiență laptopul ar trebui să aibă deja Flutter instalat înainte de începerea study jamului pentru a economisi timp. Poți aduce un laptop cu Windows / Linux / Mac. Accesați: https://flutter.dev/docs/get-started/install

Agenda:
18:00: Flutter Introduction
18:30: Break
18:45: Write Your First Flutter App, part 1
21:00: Event ends

events.name: Community Speedrun Challenge #1: BigQuery Basics for Data Analysts

venue.name: Chamber of Commerce and Industry Maramures

events.description:
Hello!

We’re sure most of you have learning new technologies and tools. That’s why we’re excited to participate in the the first Community Speedrun Challenge that Google is organizing for developer communities in Europe. And as part of the GDG Baia Mare, you’re among the first to know about this!!

The Community Speedrun Challenge is a training program that will run in February where you’ll have the opportunity to join four Speedruns and get hands-on experience with tools like Kubernetes, Assistant, BigQuery our Cloud Run. Every Speedrun is open for a week to give you the ability to finish all labs in your best time, scoring more points and winning prizes.

Find more information and register here:
https://bit.ly/speedrunchallenge0220

Schedule:
Speedrun Start Dates: February 3, 10, 17 and 24
Topics
BigQuery Basics for Data Analysts
https://google.qwiklabs.com/quests/69

Kubernetes in the Google Cloud
https://www.qwiklabs.com/quests/29

Google Developer Essentials
https://www.qwiklabs.com/quests/86?catalog_rank=%7B%22rank%22%3A1%2C%22num_filters%22%3A0%2C%22has_search%22%3Atrue%7D&search_id=4296761

Hello Cloud Run
https://google.qwiklabs.com/focuses/5162?catalog_rank=%7B%22rank%22%3A1%2C%22num_filters%22%3A0%2C%22has_search%22%3Atrue%7D&parent=catalog&search_id=3527997

Agenda
7:00 pm Welcome!
7:05 pm Speedrun Challenge explanation
7:15 pm Lab #1
8:00 pm Break & Networking
8:15 pm Lab #2
9:00 pm Next Steps & Thank You!

upcoming.name: Firebase Study Jam - Get to know Firebase for Web
upcoming.description:
Join a community of like-minded developers and explore the latest Firebase for Web technologies as a team.

Build a web app from scratch with Firebase and Stackblitz's online editor. We'll be using basic HTML and JavaScript to talk to Firebase. This is a great intro to using the Firebase console and integrating Firebase into an app. No extensive prior knowledge or software installations needed.

Bring a laptop and charger (PC, Mac or Chromebook)! The labs will run on all of the latest versions of popular browsers.
For the best experience check out Get Started with Firebase for Web. Don’t forget your charger.
